The Road Home;;90;;89;;G;;City businessman Luo Yusheng returns to his home village in North China for the funeral of his father, the village teacher. Before returning to the city, Yusheng symbolically honors his father's dearest wish: he spends one day teaching in the village school.;;Drama;;Yimou Zhang;;1999;;Zhang Ziyi,Honglei Sun,Yulian Zhao,Bin Li,Guifa Chang,Wencheng Sung,Qi Liu,Bo Ji,Zhongxi Zhang;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1108624-road_home